{"tid":108824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[真正支那狗] 支那國連狗也扮假乞兒","createTime":"2017-02-05T14:16:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T15:03:52.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca71cbcf7f9911170a83d6cf17a77fdced699b32","tid":108824,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:16:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170205/19918714?_ga=1.184614441.1297918869.1486294421\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170205%2F19918714%3F_ga%3D1.184614441.1297918869.1486294421&d=mFE05qKCD2WHpL72sA8m65ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=ba1c4edd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170205%2F19918714%3F_ga%3D1.184614441.1297918869.1486294421&h=bf221631\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170205/19918714?_ga=1.184614441.1297918869.1486294421</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/video/20170205/org/1486232847_86e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fvideo%2F20170205%2Forg%2F1486232847_86e5.jpg&h=ed9314af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">癱狗原來係「影帝」   強國網民：似足假丐幫</span><br />\n<br />\n內地丐幫假裝殘疾行乞的手法，屢見不鮮，估不到連狗狗也有此等演技！網上近日流傳一段影片，影片開頭可見，一隻後腿殘疾的狗狗，在馬路上艱難地爬行，但當好心人停車靠近時，這隻狗狗的後腿竟然直立起來，正常行走。<br />\n<br />\n不過網民看到影片後留言感嘆：「中國的乞丐，太形象了」、「專業假車禍，後來發現了有監視攝影機」、「出門在外必須一項技能」、「人生如戲全靠演技」、「13億中國人看了都流淚了」，有人則調侃：「只是腿麻而已吧」、「第一次上了那麼時間的廁所。真累」！這段廣傳的片段在內地網路廣傳，未有透露拍攝的時間、地點，有網民亦懷疑片段不是在內地拍攝，而是來自泰國的片段。"},{"pid":"d9dabe9926b52f5961f434628f1f24b40f38f483","tid":108824,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T15:03:52.000Z","msg":"On9依段片好耐以前睇過，肯定唔係支那，而且佢冇扮乞衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}